#: {{syn|ja|水瘡|tr=mizugasa}}
# {{defdate|date unspecified}} a {{m|ja|家紋|tr=kamon|t=family crest}} containing crabs, a [[front]]-[[facing]] crab in a [[circle]], and [[square]] crabs
# {{defdate|date unspecified}} a [[head]] in {{m|ja|人形浄瑠璃|tr=ningyōjōruri}} whose [[face]] is stretched out like a crab; two is used for [[honest]] [[man|men]] and another for [[minor]] [[character|characters]]
